summaries.short: Hugo and Fig want to cook dinner for their parents; plus, Hugo practices so much that he loses his ability to toot.
summaries.full: Hugo and Fig want to cook dinner for their parents, but the kitchen jobs are too dangerous. Can Esme and Roy find a way for them to help? Plus, Hugo is practicing for the Noisy Parade, and practices so much that he loses his ability to toot. How can Esme and Roy help Hugo get his toots back?
